data.title: – Vinegar Syndrome
data.text:
Please standby while we prepare for our Totally Rad! Labor Day Sale.

Our website will reopen at exactly 12:01 AM EDT on Friday, August 30th for the start of Vinegar Syndrome's Totally Rad! Labor Day Sale, featuring:

• A massive selection of discounted products, up to 75% off SRP! Including: home video releases, merchandise and clothing.

• A fresh batch of OOP titles will drop each day at 12:01 PM EDT.

• Customers who reach certain spending levels during the event, will receive free VS Media Club rewards in the form of exclusive posters designed by Steak Mtn.

• A mind-bending batch of brand new Vinegar Syndrome and Partner Label releases will be dropping during the sale on Sunday, September 1st at 12:01 PM EDT.

• PLUS: new clothing, books, merch and so much more!

Only here at VinegarSyndrome.com!

* * *

For more information, visit our Totally Rad! Labor Day Sale FAQ.
